config.script:
#Get selected local
	local = self.parent.parent.getChild("List").props.value
	
	#check if local is not null
	if local != "" and local is not None:
		#send command to add local 
		messageType = "addLocal"
		payload = {'local':local}
		system.perspective.sendMessage(messageType, payload,scope="page")
	else:
		#close popup
		id = 'AddLanguage'
		system.perspective.closePopup(id)
